REM Title: Current Wi-Fi info
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Prints the connected SSID, BSSID, channel, and RSSI via the
REM airport CLI helper.
REM Target: macOS (airport binary path stable on 10.10+)
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING /System/Library/PrivateFrameworks/Apple80211.framework/Versions/Current/Resources/airport -I
ENTER
